4
00:00:34,932 --> 00:00:36,103
Dojae...

5
00:00:38,575 --> 00:00:39,640
Who...

6
00:00:41,635 --> 00:00:42,509
...are you?

7
00:00:50,450 --> 00:00:51,818
It's prosopagnosia.

8
00:00:52,056 --> 00:00:53,882
Also called face blindness.

9
00:00:54,198 --> 00:00:56,390
The shock has damaged the temporal lobe.

10
00:00:57,527 --> 00:00:58,847
Face blindness?

11
00:00:58,932 --> 00:01:00,131
It may sound strange,

12
00:01:00,582 --> 00:01:01,795
but to make it easier,

13
00:01:03,030 --> 00:01:04,662
a part of the temporal lobe,

14
00:01:04,898 --> 00:01:07,601
which recognizes the face,
doesn't work anymore.

15
00:01:08,371 --> 00:01:09,754
Is it temporary?

16
00:01:09,839 --> 00:01:12,439
I'm afraid in this case,
there is no full treatment.

17
00:01:13,513 --> 00:01:15,275
That's when I realized...

18
00:01:27,753 --> 00:01:28,822
I'm sorry.

19
00:02:09,382 --> 00:02:11,518
...it's not the world that has changed...

20
00:02:12,242 --> 00:02:13,233
...it's me.

21
00:02:36,156 --> 00:02:37,227
Number One?

22
00:02:41,018 --> 00:02:41,885
Number Two?

23
00:02:48,049 --> 00:02:48,935
Number Three?

