705
00:44:32,751 --> 00:44:35,589
Look at the situation right now
and see if that's possible!

706
00:44:35,674 --> 00:44:38,370
Does it make sense to take a week off
considering the situation we're in now?

707
00:44:38,455 --> 00:44:41,371
